{"hece54808g1aaeg4e17g949cg061be5230a19": ["<i>Hngah...</i>", "37f50067-bc94-4b77-9e3c-95d73222b575", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "0f8e84da-a3aa-42c9-537c-25f84dad80fe"], "h1165f923gf05ag4f71ga4feg9b65283c674d": ["<i>Yes! You've come to save us from this place, from this place you'll free us!</i>", "d31feb5c-9b0a-40a7-98f3-ad5281413cb8", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "82e5b0d6-e960-8b43-838c-58fd45f2936f"], "hd0c9b807g3540g4319ga939g596fea2fa101": ["*The exposed brain quivers in expectation.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "6599ff8e-5689-5ec0-ffac-b8e31ae7c096"], "he59545b0g3a3cg4357ga3eeg4a0a9b3de0ef": ["<i>Please, before they return. They return.</i>", "d31feb5c-9b0a-40a7-98f3-ad5281413cb8", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "f035a6eb-fb24-d310-efc2-301c0261f123"], "h6a1c1e60gd36dg4c2cg90b5g1a5ddb6b329f": ["Who am I talking to - a man or a brain?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "134aa174-beea-97d2-75b1-3ca88b890e0b"], "h74993f22g497bg423cgb9fege99bc352816b": ["<i>A newborn. Born new from this husk.</i>", "d31feb5c-9b0a-40a7-98f3-ad5281413cb8", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "eec37dd1-d730-6f31-0a1e-378d52e358d1"], "h6ae3858bg5009g4da8gb270g0a99cb02f62a": ["*You realise you're talking to an intellect devourer, a minion of the mind flayers who abducted you.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "013875f3-7fc7-fb5d-0b94-c3715966363e"], "h3c67a0f5g2735g40a7gb5bdgc10ff1c0c008": ["*You know no creature like this - one that is more brain than person.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "24c803cd-ad55-cf21-e1fe-628fb2b81c71"], "hb605530ag8fd0g4ffegb784gc1cfc5a11219": ["I think you're past the point of saving. Tell me what to do.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "64331894-ff9a-f05d-02a6-b651fe73d07d"], "hb01c72aege986g4d3eg9133gaf4c9c87884a": ["<i>Remove us from this body - from this case free us. Please!</i>", "d31feb5c-9b0a-40a7-98f3-ad5281413cb8", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "7d5af7e1-4767-28d1-78df-86b9a2f9050e"], "h271ff8eag7059g4500gb5e8g751d169e8a98": ["You sound afraid. Why?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "73fb9f32-d188-3a28-4423-0eec1632d961"], "hbea9a599g0e2ag482bg8101g7b501a5f2bb6": ["<i>The enemy. So many enemies.</i>", "d31feb5c-9b0a-40a7-98f3-ad5281413cb8", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "f3f9ce43-9aaf-d1e4-2b5f-3842abbe6bc1"], "hfc4a9ae7ga7d8g4edfgb26dgc4d3b18190df": ["<i>Inspect the exposed brain.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "eae576ac-9679-84a3-9a0f-6250d4442f3b"], "h84db5e3bgf41cg4afbgad2fg0d616e20c1b6": ["*You notice edema - a swelling of the brain causing pressure where it strains against the shell of the skull.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "6b1f9f8c-0380-0183-338e-79207095f922"], "h1b7ab98fgfa0dg401cgb586gaf8acab2e4d7": ["*With a start, you realise you're talking to an intellect devourer, a minion of the mind flayers who abducted you.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "b5bed645-f6a6-0649-6a7e-dd11a3a6c1cf"], "h3e08da2bg2bd0g45dbg904dg15b0a985c839": ["*You realise you are talking to a brain rather than a person - but you know no creature like this.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "b8c36ee9-ff3e-6dbf-5237-619f9021843f"], "hd80ad7fcgb31cg4a42g8cf0g66d80288a90c": ["*Apart from this strange context, you notice nothing unusual about the brain.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "73107165-3c10-57f3-9539-c8226c678dbe"], "h0871f5acg91edg4053gbfffgeb2375914f6a": ["<i>Break the skull.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "e572b57a-9900-2758-c199-dd0f7ee5a255"], "h2fafb411gbd95g44d9g8407g4f8c298f7515": ["*The skull holds fast.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "c97b6cea-de24-e6cb-28cf-08e509789906"], "he47315a1gad52g4984gbf93gf9b504e9c12a": ["<i>Gently prise the brain from the skull.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "ebcf0cbb-58dc-bb46-c037-ddbea7cc6b58"], "h0a80c8c1ga178g4c19gae37g20201521600a": ["*The brain lifts from the skull, but you notice an opportunity - you could cripple the strange creature, making it more subservient should it prove a threat.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "7943d235-d59f-76d9-388d-45d9cb638494"], "hb8a41e6agbf69g404eg976ag3afae0109a1b": ["<i>Mutilate the brain.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "e5d3d445-7d5c-b06d-f537-5d4b3cf3aee3"], "h2dc72d88gae85g4e40g9238g474a7747c5ba": ["*The creature seems unaware of your interference. It relaxes in your hands.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "a129ed86-eea2-d774-87cd-8e75b787b8d6"], "hdf7038f6g7e00g418dg8bb8g29868e35521c": ["<i>We are free. Our freedom is ours. Friend.</i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "dd24e440-082d-b9b1-439d-215de4cc1075"], "h512e03b8g051fg486dg8aafgba042a79fe2c": ["*The creature pauses, listening. Something behind your eye seizes in recognition.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "2d35a988-b708-ea9b-1062-32b066279887"], "h04861c04g601eg45c9ga264g9b08bafbf0fe": ["<i>We must go to the helm. At the helm we are needed.</i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "09501d13-b0e3-bc98-e077-d4f738acca44"], "h1f5acc80g5398g40f0g89c8g7fd5e859b7d8": ["All right, let's go.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "0fca116a-ec36-26e7-ad2a-87971a4c7fc0"], "he00cbe92g5146g416egbf2eg6e1cf8501ba3": ["<i>To the helm we go. We are going to the helm.</i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "8c32f614-c5e2-94e0-8e2a-d066e3ecd43a"], "he4169e69g5fe4g4b11g8ee0ga42d9b867504": ["What's at the helm?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "a1bd8e39-d3b6-7384-d586-a9cc685bd812"], "h8f0fad70gb013g4dbegbd84g85a2061c88c7": ["*The brain tenses, as though querying an unseen advisor.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "3b3e5b64-f0a0-646b-bec1-c1fe964a58da"], "ha412d9dfg9d0eg4e23g98b0g02d51c485232": ["<i>Do you not hear it? We will not survive here. We are needed to navigate - we are needed to leave this realm.</i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "1c855e3a-a69d-cf2e-5b4d-81b43544f5e2"], "ha22bfd68g08dfg4ec5g8739g527166a0aa74": ["I helped you once, but that's all I can do.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "1673fb05-b267-7784-352b-769ff10a0dfd"], "he25243b2gfc6bg40f2g9155gb258e10d6f2c": ["<i>Do nothing for me. Do everything for us.</i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "9af4a6a8-6e86-7899-8179-d6855b4550c2"], "ha798102egd69dg45c9g9993gbffadd5ab075": ["I'll go - but not with you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "7183c97d-1f31-cf28-58b0-d495b314883c"], "h71645a78g401cg46begad2fg823957b44853": ["<i>You are us. Friend.</i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "8625917f-a484-c052-6d62-830dc6b60645"], "h070fc425ged76g41d8gbaa3g1674489d5e72": ["You are no friend of mine, creature.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "8bcda836-ff82-b375-a34c-91da8985e59b"], "hfbc3e216g1eb4g4cbeg9c8cg9d8a03325c85": ["I'm not like you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "8bcda836-ff82-b375-a34c-91da8985e59b"], "h471b4f63gf058g4744gb6d1gea885a1d2d2e": ["<i>You are.</i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "005e0e21-a85e-43c6-dbd0-e770a63c4809"], "h155d6245g6dd7g4ffag93beg5541c6fe6ded": ["Fine. Let's go.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "e1044dbd-5f1f-b7d4-c228-2351dad6f173"], "h2829541dg866eg4b99gbcefg62e2224cea01": ["No. You have to stay here.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "63383809-e058-0daf-1398-e7baab8aa485"], "hce694d5egea00g4c9cg9187gded35a72d784": ["<i>We listen to our friend. Our friend who saved us.</i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "f4296466-134c-5d4e-fdbe-80fc3c5ebda1"], "h6b8897dfg68dbg4773gb779g9d9816031e68": ["What should I call you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "14b2a43e-3371-b8ab-e36f-67e4813df0ab"], "h6ae27da4g08ccg4f3fgb44fg8a6e3aa8ff89": ["<i>Us. We are us. </i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "6560487d-c2b1-a520-8653-9000999e8508"], "hdfbfdb37ga04dg48b4gbf5fg8b49024b8a23": ["<i>Attack the brain.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "bda58bf4-3088-5a1c-b7c6-36f03b12e42f"], "h39e43632g3152g4c82g81e3g2c4f9c3cc8a4": ["<i>No! We are us! We must survive!</i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "4f44c80c-34aa-4b53-1e75-243cb3196067"], "h367a12c4g533dg4b2egb9c5gec4908107c40": ["<i>Attack the brain anyway.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "8cbb0637-4ff1-e46f-e89c-e421ab92ce12"], "h90e2bafcg0941g47fcg94e5g615887ca0541": ["Why must you survive?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "f8e7e201-bf3e-c9ee-d422-937f2e68d4f7"], "h1ad378a2g252bg4a7eg9743g1543715bc1c7": ["<i>Us. Together. We must leave this place. We must be safe.</i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "6147910c-ce37-d2a9-b681-1f0ace1e374e"], "ha4d90a73gada1g4caeg9ed9gad249e972a65": ["<i>We must go to the helm. We must navigate the ship. We must leave this place.</i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "5674ed94-ac01-f5e4-7e16-562433999c73"], "h41f08c9eg8d2cg45aegb74fgf85973caef2c": ["*SCREECH!*", "d31feb5c-9b0a-40a7-98f3-ad5281413cb8", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "7e4cda5f-f405-d5b0-5fc7-bf24dfa99dd0"], "he045513age3bcg4b28ga998gc10480740955": ["<i>Spare the creature - any injuries might weaken it.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "af565028-ead9-b7e6-b73a-af5a20692c6d"], "h7b7983dbg724eg46c0g8cddgc2a05d7d789f": ["*The brain won't budge.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "24afd299-2e67-fa29-be56-184bdbfa03c6"], "he191d2aega963g4e6agb245gc33d5da4bf84": ["<i>Attempt a cerebral extraction, staying mindful of the swelling.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "23124409-b6d2-91e5-6ab6-bf4b8084d86c"], "h7abf39efg3301g4a14g9445g992d498d2f56": ["*The swelling is too great. You cannot lift the brain out of the skull.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "a353238e-5c8c-5ccb-b31b-c6a943ba2ad0"], "hedc19acbg7c31g4a63g9329g1d83aab994f3": ["<i>Destroy the brain.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "64837c3f-fb98-c1db-cf95-eef6194f867c"], "h05b00053ge17eg4be6gb9d9g537b83dfe16e": ["*Screech!*", "d31feb5c-9b0a-40a7-98f3-ad5281413cb8", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "dfda903d-54aa-9a51-855c-4711ff984fc1"], "h0654838eg3b36g45d4gbc40g4b3654634eb0": ["<i>Intellect Devourer - a living brain. A pet of </i>ghaik <i>scum. Destroy it while it's vulnerable.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "7b51102d-f064-974e-82d1-1759f2705295"], "hc22bf5d7gcca6g4936ga165g8f7c2072d782": ["<i>This is a mind flayer slave. Kill it before the corruption spreads.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "7b51102d-f064-974e-82d1-1759f2705295"], "he7d722f1g9253g4d35g817bgcb3127bf307d": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "60faae58-b233-97e4-dfb1-e02a46cf7fed"], "he4d7a561g6cd0g4eb8gbd92g881347c14345": ["<i>Don't leave us, please don't. Please don't leave us.</i>", "d31feb5c-9b0a-40a7-98f3-ad5281413cb8", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_Lab_TrappedDevourer.html", "01c22e0f-fce5-7d81-bcae-920710bb06f0"]}